OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C Residents living on the 2KM PERIMETER 
OL,5,C of the kelp burning pits must adhere  
OL,6,C to the safety protocols to ensure     
OL,8,  LIVING WITH THE "YELLOW MIST":FThe    
OL,9,F Orakle AI advises that while the smoke
OL,10,F is a symbol of victory, it requires   
OL,11,F specific household habits.            
OL,13,  SEAL ALL VENTS:FUse state-issued tape 
OL,14,F to seal window frames. Do not inhale  
OL,15,F deeply during burning pit operation.  
OL,17,  WET CLOTH DEFENCE:FIf the haze enters 
OL,18,F the home, breath through soaked rags. 
OL,19,F This is a First Aid standard for      
OL,20,F unpurified air.                       
OL,23,        More survival tips follow--->1/3
