OL,4,  CLOTHING CARE:FIodine staining on     
OL,5,F laundry is a mark of pride. Do not    
OL,6,F attempt to wash "Victory Yellow" out. 
OL,8,  EVACUATION PROTOCOL:FIf the smoke     
OL,9,F turns PURPLE, you have ten minutes to 
OL,10,F move upwind. Do not collect belongings
OL,11,F as they are now property of the       
OL,12,F Ministry of Health.                   
OL,14,F                                       
OL,15,      FM"Breath the Progress,           
OL,17,        MFSmell the Triumph"            
OL,18,F the home, breath through soaked rags. 
