OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C NEW RECYCLING INITIATIVE:FThe Ministry
OL,5,CFof Sustainability is launching a new  
OL,6,CFprogram to recycle discarded breathing
OL,7, Ffilters. Collection points will be    
OL,8,F established throughout the Smoke Zone.
OL,9,F Residents are encouraged to           
OL,10,F participate.                          
OL,12,  SMOKE ZONE CHILDCARE UPDATE:FDue to   
OL,13,F increased demand. additional spaces   
OL,14,F are now available at the Ministry     
OL,15,F approved childcare facilities within  
OL,16,F the Smoke Zone. Apply by Telescreen.  
OL,18,  VICTORY GARDEN:FBoost your crop with  
OL,19,F quality kelp ash and participate in   
OL,20,F the Victory Garden Challenge.         
OL,21,F     \M"Growing for Victory!"          
